message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - This paper deals with the integration of access and backhaul in 5G cellular networks using mmWave communication, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the analysis of bandwidth partitioning and downlink rate coverage probability, which are topics related to information theory and communication, making cs.IT (Information Theory) the second likely category. The use of mmWave communication is also a topic related to multimedia and image processing, making cs.MM (Multimedia) the third likely category. The paper also deals with communication protocols and standards, which is a topic related to computer communication and networks, making cs.COMM (Computer Communication and Networks) the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper involves the study of the performance of cellular networks, which is a topic related to systems and control, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) the fifth likely category.
